description: No other experience is necessary Ð anyone can do Capoeira. Classes mix individual and group exercises to accommodate each participantÕs stage of progress. First-timers and beginners are always welcome to drop in and join any of the Beginners classes. description: This class is perfect for the beginner level dancer ages 16-35 who are looking to learn the fundamentals of hip hop dance as well as to pick up basic rhythm and coordination while getting a good workout. In this class, steps will be broken down for easy learning and many styles will be covered from week to week to give the student a wide variety of moves to and grooves to put to music and practice at home. From Old school to New school, Krump, Waacking, House and Pop there is something for everyone in this high energy, fun filled hip hop class!

This 1-hour class starts with 30 minutes of stretching, and then dives into practicing different yogic breathing techniques (Pranayama) that will strengthen the heart, lungs, core, cleanse the body of toxins, increase vitality, and sharpen the mind. The body is then completely prepared for meditation. Each week will have a different style of practice, but for all, the purpose is to give time and space for increased presence and connection to self. This class will refuel your body, mind, and spirit in every way.
